# agentclip — Cursor rules

See AGENTS.md for the authoritative project guide.

- TypeScript-first. Cloudflare Workers + Hono for the API. React + Vite for the dashboard.
- Keep API, MCP, and OAuth in a single Worker (apps/api).
- Never commit secrets; use `.dev.vars` locally and `wrangler secret put` in prod.
- All data access must be scoped by user_id. Tokens are stored as SHA-256 hashes only.
- Prefer the Web Crypto API (no extra crypto deps) inside the Worker.
